'''阿尔米拉·斯克里普琴科'''（Almira Skripchenko，{{bd|1976年|2月17日}}），[[法国|法国]]女子[[国际象棋|国际象棋]]棋手，国际大师、女子特级大师。

斯克里普琴科出生于[[摩尔多瓦|摩尔多瓦]]，6岁起开始学棋。<ref name="PL">{{cite web|last=Derbyshire|first=Martin|url=http://www.pokerlistings.com/checkmate-chess-master-skripchenko-finds-the-felt-44353|title=Checkmate: Chess master Skripchenko finds the felt|date=October 5, 2009|website=PokerListings.com|publisher=Rock Intention Malta|location=Gzira, Malta|accessdate=August 15, 2014|archive-date=2020-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200814041849/https://www.pokerlistings.com/checkmate-chess-master-skripchenko-finds-the-felt-44353|dead-url=no}}</ref>1992年，她获得世界国际象棋女子16岁组冠军。<ref>[http://brasilbase.pro.br/w16g1992.htm Duisburg 1992 - 10° World Championship u16 (girls)] {{Wayback|url=http://brasilbase.pro.br/w16g1992.htm |date=20171201044232 }} BrasilBase</ref>

1997年，斯克里普琴科与法国[[国际象棋特级大师|国际象棋特级大师]][[若埃尔·洛捷|若埃尔·洛捷]]结婚后前往法国定居。两人于2002年离婚，不过她获得了法国国籍并继续在法国居住。2007年，她与另一位法国特级大师[[洛朗·弗雷西内|洛朗·弗雷西内]]结婚。<ref>{{cite web|title=C.to Mondiale U18 femminile|url=http://www.torneionline.com/loto_tornei_d.php?codice=1993SVK10&tipo=1|website=LOTO - Lost Tournaments|publisher=Italian Chess Federation|accessdate=7 November 2015|archive-date=2014-01-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140102132545/http://www.torneionline.com/loto_tornei_d.php?codice=1993SVK10&tipo=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>

斯克里普琴科于2001年夺得欧洲国际象棋女子个人冠军。<ref>{{cite news|last=McClain|first=Dylan Loeb|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/05/04/crosswords/chess/04chess.html|title=Frenchwoman Wins Attention at an Event Dominated by Men|date=May 4, 2008|newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|location=New York City, New York|accessdate=August 15, 2014|archive-date=2018-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180805160656/https://www.nytimes.com/2008/05/04/crosswords/chess/04chess.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>她还是2004年、2005年、2006年、2010年、2012年、2015年六度法国国际象棋女子冠军。

除国际象棋之外，斯克里普琴科还是一位[[德州扑克|德州扑克]]选手，参加过[[世界扑克大赛|世界扑克大赛]]、[[世界扑克巡回赛|世界扑克巡回赛]]等比赛<ref name="PL" /><ref>{{cite web|author=<!--Staff writer(s); No by-line-->|url=http://www.wsop.com/tournaments/results.asp?tid=7261&grid=607|title=No-Limit Hold'em (Event 36)|date=June 20, 2009|website=wsop.com|publisher=Caesers Interactive Entertainment|location=Las Vegas, Nevada|accessdate=August 14, 2014|archive-date=2017-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170325135741/http://www.wsop.com/tournaments/results.asp?grid=607&tid=7261|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Perelman|first=Rob|url=http://www.commercetournaments.com/2011/03/la-poker-classic-2011-event-44-wpt.html|title=LA Poker Classic 2011 Event #44 WPT Invitational Final Results|website=Commercetournaments.com|date=March 3, 2011|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120320225211/http://www.commercetournaments.com/2011/03/la-poker-classic-2011-event-44-wpt.html|archivedate=March 20, 2012|accessdate=August 15, 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Holloway|first=Chad|url=http://www.pokernews.com/news/2011/05/world-poker-tour-on-fsn-the-wpt-celebrity-invitational-part--10486.htm|title=World Poker Tour on FSN: The WPT Celebrity Invitational Part II|date=May 30, 2011|website=[[PokerNews|PokerNews.com]]|accessdate=August 15, 2014|archive-date=2020-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200821033643/https://www.pokernews.com/news/2011/05/world-poker-tour-on-fsn-the-wpt-celebrity-invitational-part--10486.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，获得过超过250,000美元的奖金。<ref>{{cite web|author=<!--Staff writer(s); No by-line-->|url=http://pokerdb.thehendonmob.com/player.php?a=r&n=3291|title=Almira Skripchenko|website=[[The_Hendon_Mob#Other_ventures|Hendon Mob database]]|publisher=Media Rex Enterprises|accessdate=August 15, 2014|archive-date=2021-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210516075903/https://pokerdb.thehendonmob.com/player.php?a=r&n=3291|dead-url=no}}</ref>同时，她亦是一位[[将棋_(日本)|将棋]]棋手。<ref>[http://madoka-shogi.com/activit